  Inductive is_subformula_of_ind : Pattern -> Pattern -> Prop :=
  | sub_eq Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ : Ï•â‚ = Ï•â‚‚ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚
  | sub_app_l Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ : is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ (patt_app Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ)
  | sub_app_r Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ : is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚ƒ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ (patt_app Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ)
  | sub_imp_l Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ : is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ (patt_imp Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ)
  | sub_imp_r Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ : is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚ƒ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ (patt_imp Ï•â‚‚ Ï•â‚ƒ)
  | sub_exists Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ : is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ (patt_exists Ï•â‚‚)
  | sub_mu Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ : is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ -> is_subformula_of_ind Ï•â‚ (patt_mu Ï•â‚‚)
  .

  Fixpoint is_subformula_of Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚ : bool :=
    (decide_rel (=) Ï•â‚ Ï•â‚‚)
    || match Ï•â‚‚ with
       | patt_app l r | patt_imp l r => is_subformula_of Ï•â‚ l || is_subformula_of Ï•â‚ r
       | patt_exists phi | patt_mu phi => is_subformula_of Ï•â‚ phi
       | _ => false
       end.
